    <item>
      <title>字节跳动将在印度尼西亚裁员 450 人，以应对 Tokopedia 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bytedance-to-cut-450-jobs-in-indonesia-after-tokopedia-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自今年 1 月将 TikTok Shop 与当地竞争对手 Tokopedia 合并以来，字节跳动有限公司首次进行了裁员，其印尼电商部门裁员约 450 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bytedance-to-cut-450-jobs-in-indonesia-after-tokopedia-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 03:26:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑对中国获取人工智能芯片施加更多限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/us-weighss-more-limits-on-china-s-access-to-ai-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，拜登政府正在考虑进一步限制中国获取人工智能芯片技术。知情人士告诉我们，美国官员瞄准的是现在才刚刚进入市场的新硬件。尼克·特纳在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/us-weighss-more-limits-on-china-s-access-to-ai-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 00:37:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星任命苹果 Siri 资深人士领导北美 AI 集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/samsung-taps-apple-siri-veteran-to-lead-north-american-ai-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，三星电子公司正在合并两个专注于人工智能技术的北美研究中心，并聘请前苹果公司高管来管理新部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/samsung-taps-apple-siri-veteran-to-lead-north-american-ai-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 22:37:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甲骨文股价因订单量好于预期而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/oracle-shares-jump-on-better-than-expected-bookings-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甲骨文的剩余履约义务总额（衡量未来合同销售额的指标）在第四财季增长了 44%，达到 980 亿美元。分析师平均估计为 739 亿美元。阿比盖尔·杜利特尔在“彭博收盘价”中对这些数字进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/oracle-shares-jump-on-better-than-expected-bookings-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 21:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊承诺投资 14 亿美元建造 14,000 套经济适用房</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/amazon-commits-1-4-billion-to-build-14-000-affordable-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司承诺向其住房股权基金投入 14 亿美元，继续支持西雅图、纳什维尔和华盛顿大都市区的经济适用房。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/amazon-commits-1-4-billion-to-build-14-000-affordable-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 21:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克撤回对 OpenAI 违反创始使命的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/musk-drops-suit-accusing-openai-of-breaching-founding-mission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克撤回了一项诉讼，指控 OpenAI 及其首席执行官萨姆·奥特曼去年违反了创始承诺，将利润置于人类之上——但没有说明原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/musk-drops-suit-accusing-openai-of-breaching-founding-mission</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 20:42:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甲骨文股价大涨，交易证明其云计算业务发展顺利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/oracle-reports-strong-bookings-signaling-further-cloud-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甲骨文公司 (Oracle Corp.) 公布的订单量好于预期，并宣布与科技竞争对手达成合作协议，这为董事长拉里·埃里森 (Larry Ellison) 将这家软件制造商重新定位为云计算业务的主要竞争对手的努力提供了助力。该公司股价在盘后交易中上涨逾 9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/oracle-reports-strong-bookings-signaling-further-cloud-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 20:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果股价创 2022 年以来最大涨幅，因希望人工智能能推动升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/apple-hits-first-record-this-year-on-hopes-ai-will-fuel-upgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对这家 iPhone 制造商的信心持续改善，苹果公司股价周二上涨，创下自 12 月以来的首次新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/apple-hits-first-record-this-year-on-hopes-ai-will-fuel-upgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 14:13:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果推出“为我们其他人而设的人工智能”创下纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/apple-unveils-iphone-os-at-ai-focused-developers-conference</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 公布了人们期待已久的全新人工智能功能后，其股价创下新高，该公司认为，个性化、低调的技术方式将赢得客户的青睐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/apple-unveils-iphone-os-at-ai-focused-developers-conference</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:31:51 GMT</pubDate>
